   Situational Awareness for Fire Fighters  
    SAFIRE  (funding by DHS / FEMA) utilzes next generation information technology
   to bring situational awareness to Incident Commanders. We make use of a variety of sensors (e.g., CO, acuostic,
   motes), networks, and visualization capabilities to provide information to and from first responders. 
      
   
    
    
